Today, through the Franciscan, others experience it.
For Masses celebrated by Fr Witko for the release and healing bring crowds
Once upon a time, the parents of a seven-month-old child who had a hole of 7.5 mm in her heart.
It was supposed to be operated on.
Father Joseph Witko prayed for him.
On the same day, the boy was taken to the hospital for surgery.
Astonished doctors said: "Operation is not needed, loss is only 1.5 mm".
My parents were crying out of happiness.
After another prayer, the Franciscan hole disappeared completely.
The Creator’s spiritual remarkable actions began to be experienced as a teenager.
In his dreams, purgatory souls came to him asking for help.
I was awakened at night and urged to pray for the dead and those who died at that moment – he recalls.
He also experienced the presence of an evil spirit.
And he had a vision of what happens to a man who commits a mortal sin.
"My body began to change.
I've lost human qualities and started to look like an animal," he says.
The invisible force lifted him up, couldn't get his voice out of him.
He felt he was lost.
Then God showed him salvation.
"In the waters of the river symbolizing holy baptism, I was freed and returned to human form..." he says.
He didn't tell anyone about these strange experiences.
His calling was ripe.
He was 16 when he joined the Franciscans.
In his sermons, he wanted to talk more than just about Jesus.
He wanted people to experience him alive.
Members of the charismatic community of renewal in the Holy Spirit
Many people who count on getting rid of the disease participate in Masses about healing celebrated by Father Witko.
But the clergyman emphasizes that their primary goal is spiritual healing, not fleshly healing.
